Package civitas.celestis.util.collection

Interface Listable<E>

Type Parameters:
E - The type of element this object is holding
All Superinterfaces:
Collectable<E>
All Known Subinterfaces:
ArrayGroup<E>, BigVector<N,V>, DecimalVector<V>, DoubleVector<V>, FloatVector<V>, Tuple<E>, Vector<N,V>
All Known Implementing Classes:
ArrayTuple, ArrayVector, Decimal2, Decimal3, Decimal4, DecimalArrayVector, DecimalQuaternion, Float2, Float3, Float4, LinearColor, Pair, Quad, Quaternion, SafeArray, Triple, Vector2, Vector3, Vector4
public interface Listable<E> extends Collectable<E>
An interface for objects which are not a list, but can be easily converted to a list.
